<br>
I have tried 2 boxing in Chardok but that can be scary at times considering that many people over pull to the zone entrance and I often have to contend with adds.  If I can get lucky I can sometimes get the plateau camp spots in Scarlett Desert, but usually these spots are over camped so it isn't very rewarding.<br>
<br>
I have been considering a third computer so I can utilize my druid more often and perhaps I can powerlevel a chanter or cleric, but I just can't seem to convince myself to spend the money on another computer.<br>
